# MISC::GET_NEXT_WEATHER_TYPE_HASH_NAME

## Returns
* **INT**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Gets the hash name of the next weather type (the one we are currently interpolating towards)

Returns weather name hash
